, à Cagliari, Sardegna, Italie, à l’âge de 56 ans."},"de":{"environ 1160–environ 1214":"um 1160–um 1214","1160–1214":"1160–1214","1165–1206":"1165–1206","–Female":"Verstorben","–1230":"–1230","1185–1257":"1185–1257","1194–1233":"1194–1233","1090–1155":"1090–1155","1120–Female":"1120–Verstorben","from 1195 to 1206":"von 1195 bis 1206","environ 1214":"um 1214","1090":"1090","aproximadamente 1185":"um 1185","1165":"1165","1120":"1120","1230":"1230","environ 1160":"um 1160","1185":"1185","1194":"1194","1160":"1160","1206":"1206","1214":"1214","1257":"1257","1233":"1233","1155":"1155","from 1188 to 1214":"von 1188 bis 1214","Pisa, Toscana, Itália":"Pisa, Toscana, Italien","Cagliari, Sardinia, Italy":"Cagliari, Sardinien, Italien","Cagliari, Sardegna, Itália":"Cagliari, Sardinien, Italien","Santa Igia, Sardegna, ITALIA":"Sardinien, Italien","lifeSummary":"Als Guglielmo I Salusio IV di Massa, 7th Judge of Cagliari um 1160 in Pisa, Toscana, Italien geboren wurde, war sein Vater Oberto Obertenghi Marchese di Massa e di Corsica 72 und seine Mutter Giorgia di Lacon-Gunale, Marchioness of Massa 42. Er hat Adelisa Malaspina geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 3 Töchter. Er starb um 1214 im Alter von 56 Jahren in Cagliari, Sardinien, Italien."},"ht":{"environ 1160–environ 1214":"about 1160–about 1214","1160–1214":"1160–1214","1165–1206":"1165–1206","–Female":"Desede","–1230":"–1230","1185–1257":"1185–1257","1194–1233":"1194–1233","1090–1155":"1090–1155","1120–Female":"1120–Desede","from 1195 to 1206":"from 1195 to 1206","environ 1214":"about 1214","1090":"1090","aproximadamente 1185":"about 1185","1165":"1165","1120":"1120","1230":"1230","environ 1160":"about 1160","1185":"1185","1194":"1194","1160":"1160","1206":"1206","1214":"1214","1257":"1257","1233":"1233","1155":"1155","from 1188 to 1214":"from 1188 to 1214","Pisa, Toscana, Itália":"Pisa, Toscana, Itali","Cagliari, Sardinia, Italy":"Cagliari, Sardegna, Itali","Cagliari, Sardegna, Itália":"Cagliari, Sardegna, Itali","Santa Igi